<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从前，有一个非常善良的女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的名字叫艾拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和父亲过着幸福的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉有漂亮的衣服和珠宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她有一个大房间，有一张温暖、舒适的床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，家里总是有很多食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，艾拉和她父亲在镇里散步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包店里传来香味儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们买点好吃的吧。”父亲说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉看见一个年轻的乞丐坐在镇上的广场上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个男孩儿真可怜。”艾拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，我们能给他买点东西吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真善良，艾拉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲买了些面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉把面包给了那个男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您，小姐。”男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几天后，艾拉在花园里见到了父亲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看起来很开心，爸爸。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个令人兴奋的消息！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我遇到了我喜欢的女人。”父亲说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要结婚了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，我真为你高兴！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一周后，父亲结婚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾拉的继母有两个女儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大女儿又高又瘦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女儿又矮又胖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“见到你们很高兴！”艾拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女儿笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们的母亲也笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她的眼神却很不友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>